text: Hrdinové mlčí is a 1946 Czechoslovak drama film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Ladislav Boháč, Zdeněk Dítě, and František Filipovský. ==References== ==External links== *Hrdinové mlčí at the Internet Movie Database Category:1946 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak drama films Category:1946 drama films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czech war films Category:Czech resistance to Nazi occupation in film Category:Czechoslovak black-and-white films
